processors.name: Write File Attributes to the Database

entry.value: insert into siaft.Analysis values(null,(select PK_FileAttributes_ID from siaft.FileAttributes where UUID='${siaft.uuid}'),(select PK_AnalyzeEngine_ID from siaft.AnalyzeEngines where EngineName='${analysis_engine_name}'),(select PK_SanitizeEngine_ID from siaft.SanitizeEngines where EngineName='${sanitize_engine_name}'),${Analysis.Success},'${Analysis.Results}',now(),null);

processors.name: Write Analyzer Results to the Database

entry.value: insert into siaft.Sanitize values(null,(select PK_FileAttributes_ID from siaft.FileAttributes where UUID='${siaft.uuid}'),(select PK_SanitizeEngine_ID from siaft.SanitizeEngines where EngineName='${sanitize_engine_name}'),'${process_success}','${process_md5}','${process_mime}',now(),null);
